    Collects all AclLineMatchExprs of the given type built into the visited expression. Multiple expressions of the given type may be built into the visited expression if the visited expression is of type AndMatchExpr, OrMatchExpr, or NotMatchExpr. This visitor is therefore useful for finding all ACLs referenced or all header spaces contained within a single ACL line.
